        <rdfs:comment xml:lang="en">Note 1 to entry: A function may also produce other changes through the use of parameters.
Note 2 to entry: function: term and definition standardized by ISO/IEC [ISO/IEC 2382-15:1999].
Note 3 to entry: 15.06.12 (2382)
[SOURCE: ISO-IEC-2382-15 * 1999 * * * ]</rdfs:comment>
